17#ifndef _LVM_TIMESTAMP_H
18#define _LVM_TIMESTAMP_H
19
20struct timestamp;
21
22struct timestamp *get_timestamp(void);
23
24/* cmp_timestamp: Compare two timestamps
25 *
26 * Return: -1 if t1 is less than t2
27 * 0 if t1 is equal to t2
28 * 1 if t1 is greater than t2
29 */
30int cmp_timestamp(struct timestamp *t1, struct timestamp *t2);
31
32void destroy_timestamp(struct timestamp *t);
33
34#endif /* _LVM_TIMESTAMP_H */
